name: Elm-plugin
tagline: Elm language support plugin for IntelliJ IDEA.
body:
# elm-plugin
Elm language plugin for IntelliJ IDEA.

## Features

- Supports Elm 0.17.0
- Parsing the syntax
- Coloring keywords, comments, strings and numbers
- Going to declaration 
- Highlighting unresolved references
